    {
        " is often used to ensure smooth rotation or to store energy to carry the engine through an un-powered part of the cycle. The more cylinders a reciprocating engine has, generally, the more vibration-free it can operate. The power of a reciprocating engine is proportional to the volume of the combined pistons displacement.     A seal must be made between the sliding ": null
