    },
    {
        "compression ratio": "Compression Ratio"
    },
    {
        " affects the performance in most types of reciprocating engine. It is the ratio between the volume of the cylinder, when the piston is at the bottom of its stroke, and the volume when the piston is at the top of its stroke.     The ": null
